    "body": "###### Reproduction Steps\r\n\r\n1. Tap search button (appears when you have at least 10 decks)\r\n2. Close keyboard that pops up\r\n\r\n\r\n###### Expected Result\r\nThe floating action button (FAB) should disappear when a search is initiated.\r\n\r\n\r\n###### Actual Result\r\nThe FAB moves up as a small dot that is still actionable and results in a weird issue when tapped upon. It's too cramped to still appear, and when tapping on a selection, only some of the options appear depending on the screen size. If the FAB is tapped, backing out takes an extra step (3 back button taps) to exit out of the search.\r\n\r\nOn the most recent alpha, v 2.16alpha56, the FAB does not shrink in size for me, but that may be related to my emulator. Regardless, the issue still persists.\r\n\r\n\r\n###### Debug info\r\n```\r\nAnkiDroid Version = 2.15.6\r\n\r\nAndroid Version = 12\r\n\r\nManufacturer = samsung\r\n\r\nModel = SM-S901U\r\n\r\nHardware = qcom\r\n\r\nWebview User Agent = Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 12; SM-S901U Build/SP1A.210812.016; wv) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/4.0 Chrome/99.0.4844.88 Mobile Safari/537.36\r\n\r\nACRA UUID = 6513c4b2-d751-40e6-9fab-f42c1fc1e7f9\r\n\r\nScheduler = std2\r\n\r\nCrash Reports Enabled = false\r\n\r\nDatabaseV2 Enabled = true\r\n```\r\n\r\n###### Research\r\n*Enter an [x] character to confirm the points below:*\r\n\r\n- [x] I have read the [support page](https://ankidroid.org/docs/help.html) and am reporting a bug or enhancement request specific to AnkiDroid\r\n- [x] I have checked the [manual](https://ankidroid.org/docs/manual.html) and the [FAQ](https://github.com/ankidroid/Anki-Android/wiki/FAQ) and could not find a solution to my issue\r\n- [x] I have searched for similar existing issues here and on the user forum\r\n- [x] (Optional) I have confirmed the issue is not resolved in the latest alpha release ([instructions](https://docs.ankidroid.org/manual.html#betaTesting))\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/71997294/163003201-51d23947-fe74-42c3-9a87-4475d68e208a.mp4\r\n\r\nv 2.15.6\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/71997294/163004244-3f240420-abc2-4c82-b7c6-8a12138a50eb.mp4\r\n\r\nv 2.16alpha56",
